# This branch is force-mirrored to a PUBLIC GitHub repo on every push, so a
# committed secret is world-readable within about a minute and stays in history
# permanently. Credentials belong in the github-mirror variable group in Azure
# DevOps, never in this repo. See CONNECT-TO-GITBOOK.md.
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*

# OS and editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
.vscode/
.idea/
